Miscommunication between developers and testers

Low team motivation leading to slower progress

Risk Table (Probability/Impact/Response)

Risk	Probability	Impact	Response
API outage	High	High	Add fallback data cache
Data loss CSV	Medium	High	Validate input before save
Login vulnerability	Medium	High	Enforce stronger passwords
Sprint delay	High	Medium	Break work into smaller tasks
Testing delay	Medium	High	Add buffer days
Missed deadline	Low	High	Adjust timeline with sponsor
Hosting cost high	Medium	Medium	Track usage, set alerts
Extra tool cost	Medium	Medium	Approve tools early
Penalty for late release	Low	High	Communicate with sponsor
Team absence	Medium	Medium	Cross-train members
Miscommunication	High	Medium	Use daily check-ins
Low motivation	Medium	Medium	Encourage progress updates
